  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Detection and determination of platelets in bronchoalveolar lavage fluid and blood in ARDS&#xD;
      and non-ARDS-patients. Correlation with phenotype and inflammation parameters in blood and&#xD;
      outcome parameters.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
